title: Mens Fitness Magazine UK July 2012
description:
Mens Fitness Magazine UK July 2012

Men's Fitness Magazine: the national obsession with staying in shape 
continues to boom. And we know how important your fitness is to you.
Men's Fitness magazine is all about fitness--inside and out for todays 
health-conscious male who wants to gain optimum results. Each issue 
shows efficient ways to work specific body parts, get the best nutrition 
from foods, and unleash more passion for sex, relationships and adventure.
